}


### Get Task Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json


### Update Task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Update Task API",
  "description": "Update CRUD implementation",
  "assigned_to": 2,
  "due_date": "2026-05-05"
}


### Delete Task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### Update Task Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

